{"id":644245443,"lang":"java","time":"1 week, 1 day","timestamp":1645238458,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"5 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/644245443/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"42.3 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int lengthOfLongestSubstring(String s) {\n        Map<Character, Integer> map = new HashMap<>();\n        int begin = 0, end = 0, len = 0;\n        \n        while (end < s.length()) {\n            char curr = s.charAt(end);\n            \n            if (map.containsKey(curr) && map.get(curr) >= begin) {\n                begin = map.get(curr) + 1;\n            } else {\n                map.put(curr, end);\n                end++;\n            }\n            \n            if (end - begin > len) {\n                len = end - begin;\n            }\n        }\n        return len;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters"}
